						<summary>

						<p>Beginning part lost. Records a gift of land after purchase from the <hi rend="italic">sabhā</hi> of the village for offerings to the god Śivalōkaviṭaṅkadēva and the goddess, by Kīrttirājarājan <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Rājarāja-Gandaruva-mārāyaṉ. The inscription may belong to Rājēndra I (See No. 34 below).</p>						

						</summary>
